qas.question: The government structure of the New Delhi Municipal Council includes three members from what government body?
What government body is responsible for nominating five members to the New Delhi Municipal Council?
What government official is responsible for nominating two members to the New Delhi Municipal Council?

answers.text: Chief Minister of the NCT of Delhi

qas.question: The Chief Minister of what NCT is responsible for nominating two members to the New Delhi Municipal Council?
What is the name of the government structure created for New Delhi that is comprised of ten representatives?

context: As of 2015, the government structure of the <a4_0>New Delhi Municipal Council<a4_0/> includes a chairperson, three members of <a0_0>New Delhi's Legislative Assembly<a0_0/>, two members nominated by the <a2_0>Chief Minister of the <a3_0>NCT of Delhi<a3_0/><a2_0/> and five members nominated by <a1_0>the central government<a1_0/>.
